This paper deals with evaluating computational models for text understanding, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep networks, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the modification of large-scale datasets, which could also place it under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
